\begin_layout Enumerate
Before select a car, user could filter available cars by position as descripted
 in “Search a car”.
 In this case the system show him/her the nearest cars.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
User select a car from the list of available car.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system show to the user all the information about the car like the level
 of the battery.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
After that the user click on the “Confirm” button to make the reservation.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system delete the car from the list of available cars.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system start the timer of one hour.
 
\end_layout

