\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Output condition
\end_layout

\end_inset
</cell>
<cell alignment="left" valignment="middle" topline="true" leftline="true" rightline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
The system, through the external payment gateway, charges the user with
 the total cost of the ride taking care of eventual discounts.
 If the system detects that the car is parked at more than 3km from the
 nearest power grid station, it sends a notification to the nearest operator
 and charges 30% more the user.
\end_layout

\end_inset
</cell>
</row>
